            "content": "## Content Check \nReads expected email elements from Google Sheets—From address, Subject line, Preheader, Body copy, and Footer content. Extracts actual values from HTML, merges inputs, compares expected vs actual to generate the Result, and logs Actual Content + Result back to Google Sheets."
          },
